remove_from_hook

 SYNOPSIS
  Remove a function from a list of hooks

 USAGE
  remove_from_hook (String_Type hook_name, Ref_Type funct)

 DESCRIPTION
  `remove_from_hook' removes the function `funct' from the
  list of hooks associated with `hook_name'.

